  LearningObjectives1Title: Transitioning to LTC
  LearningObjectives1Text: To recognize the importance of ongoing communication with
    the inter professional team, residents and their family members.
  LearningObjectives2Title: 
  LearningObjectives2Text: To understand and respect cultural differences of each
    resident in long term care.
  LearningObjectives3Title: 
  LearningObjectives3Text: To be sensitive and empathetic that transitioning from
    community to long term care can be a challengeing life experience.
  BestPractices1Title: Transitioning to LTC
  BestPractices1Text: The responsibility of the care team to utilize all available
    resources in order for the resident to communicate their care needs.
  BestPractices2Title: 
  BestPractices2Text: A resident should be assessed on admission and re-assessed regularly
    to ensure that they are receiving quality care and that they are safe.
  BestPractices3Title: 
  BestPractices3Text: Offer opportunities for purposeful and meaningful activities
    that promote cultural diversity and encourage an inclusive environment in all
    aspects of the home.
